472
00:43:13,115 --> 00:43:17,819
<i>My way!</i>

473
00:43:25,423 --> 00:43:29,104
Choi Choon Hee!
Choi Choon Hee!

474
00:43:29,104 --> 00:43:32,539
- Choi Choon Hee!
- No, don't do that.

475
00:43:38,528 --> 00:43:41,122
[Dongbu Hospital]

476
00:43:43,089 --> 00:43:46,188
<i>- Is this Choi Myung Sik?</i>
- Yes, it is.

477
00:43:47,482 --> 00:43:48,927
Yes.

478
00:43:48,940 --> 00:43:50,395
You postponed your
surgery before.

479
00:43:50,395 --> 00:43:52,944
What date should I reschedule it for?

480
00:43:52,944 --> 00:43:56,067
About that...

481
00:43:56,067 --> 00:43:59,990
I don't think I can get surgery.
I'm sorry.

482
00:43:59,990 --> 00:44:02,324
You can't afford not
to get surgery at this time.

483
00:44:02,324 --> 00:44:06,224
<i>Choi Myung Sik!
Choi Myung Sik!</i>

484
00:44:16,165 --> 00:44:20,686
Joon Hyun. This came for you.

485
00:44:20,686 --> 00:44:22,956
Wow, it was...

486
00:44:23,862 --> 00:44:28,807
What's this? Jang Joon Hyun,
has your memory returned?

487
00:44:28,807 --> 00:44:31,604
Wow, this is good news!

488
00:44:31,604 --> 00:44:33,635
This is good! I'm so happy for you!

489
00:44:33,635 --> 00:44:35,463
- This is good news!
- Can you laugh right now?

490
00:44:35,463 --> 00:44:37,019
Get on your knees.

491
00:44:43,413 --> 00:44:46,675
I'm sorry.
I deserve to die.

492
00:44:48,108 --> 00:44:49,775
You deserve to die?

493
00:44:51,427 --> 00:44:53,367
For what?

494
00:44:53,367 --> 00:44:56,215
For having handed me over
to the police?

495
00:44:56,215 --> 00:45:01,446
Or not telling me about Choon Hee?
What do you think is the graver sin?

496
00:45:02,914 --> 00:45:05,331
The second?

497
00:45:06,074 --> 00:45:09,557
Forget it. There's something
you need to do for me.

498
00:45:09,557 --> 00:45:11,460
What's that?

499
00:45:12,773 --> 00:45:15,927
Keep it a secret that my memory's
returned for the time being.

500
00:45:15,927 --> 00:45:17,411
Huh?

501
00:45:17,411 --> 00:45:19,990
If Director Yang finds out, who know
what will happen to Choon Hee.

502
00:45:19,990 --> 00:45:22,836
You can keep this secret, right?

503
00:45:24,245 --> 00:45:27,384
- I got it.
- I'll kill you if you betray me again.

504
00:45:28,784 --> 00:45:32,287
I... thought you'd be better
if I did that...

505
00:45:37,236 --> 00:45:39,583
Joon Hyun, is it okay
to overwork yourself

506
00:45:39,596 --> 00:45:41,954
like this when you
were just discharged?

507
00:45:44,167 --> 00:45:45,641
- Soo In.
- Hmm?

508
00:45:47,950 --> 00:45:49,978
Just a minute.

509
00:45:57,546 --> 00:46:01,390
There's something that
I've been wanting to ask you.

510
00:46:03,313 --> 00:46:04,747
W...what's that?

511
00:46:06,408 --> 00:46:10,235
That day... the day of the accident...

512
00:46:11,483 --> 00:46:13,536
Why were you up on that stage?

513
00:46:14,463 --> 00:46:18,625
That wasn't your stage, but
Choi Choon Hee's concert.

514
00:46:20,955 --> 00:46:25,581
That... I went to cheer Choon Hee on.

515
00:46:25,581 --> 00:46:27,211
She's my junior, after all.

516
00:46:27,211 --> 00:46:29,502
I went because I should at least
be looking after her.

517
00:46:30,106 --> 00:46:32,443
I see.

518
00:46:33,865 --> 00:46:37,515
But the thing is... I keep having
these weird thoughts.

519
00:46:39,297 --> 00:46:42,390
That someone was targeting
someone else...

520
00:46:42,390 --> 00:46:45,006
and that I was hit for their sakes.

521
00:46:46,554 --> 00:46:49,736
By any chance...

522
00:46:49,736 --> 00:46:51,591
was that person was
targeting Choi Choon Hee.

523
00:46:52,262 --> 00:46:56,863
J...Joon Hyun, I don't even want
to think about that day.

524
00:46:56,863 --> 00:46:59,580
Do you know how surprised I was
when you were hurt?

525
00:46:59,580 --> 00:47:02,186
I seriously thought that
something terrible happened to you.

526
00:47:03,438 --> 00:47:07,277
All that's important to me
is that you're safe, Joon Hyun.

527
00:47:07,277 --> 00:47:10,297
If someone targeted Choi Choon Hee...

528
00:47:10,297 --> 00:47:12,090
then that's a relief.

529
00:47:14,543 --> 00:47:16,595
But someone I love.

530
00:47:18,767 --> 00:47:22,247
If they were targeting you, then I
probably couldn't stand aside.

531
00:47:24,045 --> 00:47:26,388
I'd hunt them down to the end.

532
00:47:34,355 --> 00:47:36,779
Come in.

533
00:47:47,812 --> 00:47:49,787
Come in. What brings you here?

534
00:47:50,976 --> 00:47:52,850
I came to see you, of course.

535
00:47:52,850 --> 00:47:56,602
Is that right?
Should I call Soo In over, too?

536
00:47:56,602 --> 00:47:58,346
We could all have dinner later.

537
00:47:58,346 --> 00:48:01,693
More importantly, I have something
to tell you, Director Yang.

538
00:48:02,652 --> 00:48:04,154
Go ahead.

539
00:48:05,251 --> 00:48:07,245
There's something that's been
on my mind.

540
00:48:07,245 --> 00:48:09,390
About the accident last time...

541
00:48:09,390 --> 00:48:14,313
I went to the office at the concert
because I'm superstitious.

542
00:48:14,313 --> 00:48:18,806
But it just so happened that
the CCTV cameras weren't on then.

543
00:48:20,158 --> 00:48:25,175
I lost my cellphone there too.

544
00:48:27,049 --> 00:48:28,895
And so?

545
00:48:28,895 --> 00:48:32,173
I'm thinking... that I need
to look more into it.

546
00:48:35,801 --> 00:48:39,827
Aren't you overdoing it when
your body isn't up to it yet?

547
00:48:40,472 --> 00:48:42,756
I'll look into that problem myself
from now on.

548
00:48:42,756 --> 00:48:44,460
- You...
- No.

549
00:48:45,234 --> 00:48:48,196
I'm the type who gets impatient
when I'm curious.

550
00:48:49,373 --> 00:48:51,727
I'm planning to hunt it down
myself to the end.

551
00:48:58,220 --> 00:49:00,893
But the thing is...

552
00:49:00,893 --> 00:49:08,106
Why... are you telling me
all this right now?

553
00:49:08,984 --> 00:49:10,609
What do you mean?

554
00:49:12,593 --> 00:49:16,538
We'll be a family soon, and family
shares everything with each other.

555
00:49:16,538 --> 00:49:18,776
Am I wrong, Director Yang?

556
00:49:19,692 --> 00:49:23,385
Of course... you aren't wrong.

557
00:49:28,058 --> 00:49:29,921
Mom, Joon Hyun is acting weird.

558
00:49:29,921 --> 00:49:33,787
I'll say. He keeps
asking about that day.

559
00:49:33,787 --> 00:49:34,994
He went to you, too?

560
00:49:34,994 --> 00:49:37,637
Did his memory return
and he's pretending it didn't?

561
00:49:37,637 --> 00:49:40,003
Wait a minute.

562
00:49:40,003 --> 00:49:43,431
Let's think of an order.
What's the priority.

563
00:49:50,915 --> 00:49:53,709
When will our little Byul....
She's here.

564
00:50:03,876 --> 00:50:06,282
Hey.

565
00:50:11,200 --> 00:50:13,318
- Ow!
- I heard you hit my sister!

566
00:50:14,923 --> 00:50:17,903
You! You called your older
sister like a coward?

567
00:50:17,903 --> 00:50:20,372
You little punk!
So fearless!

568
00:50:20,372 --> 00:50:22,247
Do you want to be hit?

569
00:50:22,247 --> 00:50:24,853
You little punks! So fearless!

570
00:50:24,853 --> 00:50:26,389
Do you want to be hit?

571
00:50:26,389 --> 00:50:27,714
Mister!

572
00:50:27,714 --> 00:50:31,690
Who is it? You won't let go?
Let go!

573
00:50:32,406 --> 00:50:34,137
You let go first.

574
00:50:40,072 --> 00:50:43,880
Mister, don't butt in
and be on your way.

575
00:50:43,880 --> 00:50:45,466
How annoying.

576
00:50:45,466 --> 00:50:48,696
Pick up the gum you spat out right now.

577
00:50:48,696 --> 00:50:50,316
What is he saying?

578
00:50:50,316 --> 00:50:52,596
This man, seriously...

579
00:50:52,596 --> 00:50:54,652
He doesn't know what
to be afraid of.

580
00:50:56,648 --> 00:50:59,780
Hey, who are you?

581
00:50:59,780 --> 00:51:01,837
Who are you to talk like that?

582
00:51:03,414 --> 00:51:06,144
I'm...

583
00:51:07,693 --> 00:51:11,982
Music's god... Jang Joon Hyun.

584
00:51:11,982 --> 00:51:13,912
- Oh my god!
- Ah! Joon Hyun!

585
00:51:13,912 --> 00:51:15,811
You're really Jang Joon Hyun?

586
00:51:17,158 --> 00:51:18,981
What do I do? Hit me!

587
00:51:19,399 --> 00:51:22,065
It hurts! This isn't a dream!

588
00:51:24,189 --> 00:51:25,577
Kids.

589
00:51:25,577 --> 00:51:30,602
I'm part of Byul's family, but you
seem to be giving her a hard time.

590
00:51:30,602 --> 00:51:32,928
No, no. What do you mean?

591
00:51:33,691 --> 00:51:36,155
I'm seeing this cutie
for the first time!

592
00:51:38,717 --> 00:51:41,456
My little sister is really
good friends with her!

593
00:51:41,456 --> 00:51:43,649
- Isn't that right?
- Then...

594
00:51:43,649 --> 00:51:45,689
You're going to get along
from now on, right?

595
00:51:46,923 --> 00:51:48,707
Hurry up and answer.

596
00:51:49,839 --> 00:51:50,872
Yes.

597
00:51:59,066 --> 00:52:00,854
- Should I give you an autograph?
- Yes, yes!

598
00:52:00,854 --> 00:52:03,279
- Should I take a picture with you?
- Yes!

599
00:52:03,279 --> 00:52:04,741
All right!

600
00:52:04,741 --> 00:52:07,122
- Does it taste good?
- It does.

601
00:52:09,049 --> 00:52:12,754
Byul, about today...

602
00:52:13,158 --> 00:52:16,381
I know. It's a secret
to my sister, right?

603
00:52:18,138 --> 00:52:19,313
Secret? Okay.

604
00:52:19,313 --> 00:52:20,603
Okay.

605
00:52:21,864 --> 00:52:23,767
- Bang!
- Bang!

606
00:52:23,767 --> 00:52:25,411
- Bang, bang!
- Bang, bang, bang!

607
00:52:25,411 --> 00:52:29,516
Choi Myung Sik? It's been a while
since I've seen him, too.

608
00:52:34,785 --> 00:52:36,645
Anyone home?

609
00:52:50,580 --> 00:52:52,098
Father!

610
00:52:53,243 --> 00:52:55,713
Father, are you okay?

611
00:53:10,873 --> 00:53:13,110
Here, here, here.

612
00:53:13,110 --> 00:53:15,614
It's fine. It's hot, it's hot.
Be careful.

613
00:53:16,469 --> 00:53:19,420
You haven't eaten until now?

614
00:53:19,420 --> 00:53:22,876
That's what I'm saying.
I said we should eat anywhere, but...

615
00:53:22,876 --> 00:53:29,094
For me, if I don't have the ox
bone broth you've cooked overnight

616
00:53:29,094 --> 00:53:31,855
to have this soondae soup...

617
00:53:31,855 --> 00:53:35,263
Then no matter what I eat,
it feels like I haven't eaten.

618
00:53:36,524 --> 00:53:37,977
Check, please!

619
00:53:37,977 --> 00:53:39,465
- Yes.
- Sit down.

620
00:53:39,465 --> 00:53:41,405
Coming!

621
00:53:43,425 --> 00:53:45,351
- For two, yes?
- Yes.

622
00:53:46,175 --> 00:53:48,221
Fourteen thousand Won.

623
00:53:50,585 --> 00:53:51,991
Goodbye!

624
00:54:03,879 --> 00:54:07,701
Father, are you awake now?

625
00:54:23,545 --> 00:54:27,341
In order to resolve my debts...

626
00:54:27,341 --> 00:54:30,511
I went to loan sharks and
took out a private loan.

627
00:54:32,174 --> 00:54:35,343
But then I was nearly beaten
to death by them.

628
00:54:37,139 --> 00:54:40,558
When I opened my eyes,
I was in the hospital.

629
00:54:41,870 --> 00:54:44,682
I also have colon cancer.

630
00:54:45,778 --> 00:54:52,037
I found out... that I only have
six months to live.

631
00:54:54,503 --> 00:54:57,614
I don't have the money
to pay for treatment, either.

632
00:54:58,554 --> 00:55:03,423
But I wanted to leave something
to my children before I went...

633
00:55:03,423 --> 00:55:05,819
So I started cleaning.

634
00:55:09,823 --> 00:55:12,435
But this pitiful life...

635
00:55:14,501 --> 00:55:17,713
is still breathing.

636
00:55:29,034 --> 00:55:32,436
When I was in grade school...

637
00:55:32,436 --> 00:55:38,088
I came back from school
to find out that my father had died.

638
00:55:44,699 --> 00:55:46,487
I shouldn't have gone
to school that day.

639
00:55:49,231 --> 00:55:54,486
I should have stayed by his side
for one more hour...

640
00:55:58,594 --> 00:56:04,378
You hAve no idea how
long I regretted that.

641
00:56:10,678 --> 00:56:12,812
Father.

642
00:56:13,831 --> 00:56:17,628
Choon Hee's having a really hard time
because of various scandals.

643
00:56:19,210 --> 00:56:21,934
I'm going to go back to Choon Hee.

644
00:56:21,934 --> 00:56:26,458
But before I do, couldn't you
take care of her for now?

645
00:56:31,410 --> 00:56:33,860
Even if it's just for an hour more.

646
00:56:43,465 --> 00:56:45,243
Yes.

647
00:56:46,118 --> 00:56:48,694
- President.
- Yes.

648
00:56:48,694 --> 00:56:51,708
Hello.

649
00:56:51,708 --> 00:56:54,415
I heard you had a concert
at a homeless persons' event.

650
00:56:54,415 --> 00:56:59,609
Yes, I went to help volunteer
but they were so good to me.

651
00:57:00,487 --> 00:57:04,271
It had a positive response,
so the company is going to help out.

652
00:57:04,271 --> 00:57:06,763
Oh really? That's really great news.

653
00:57:08,105 --> 00:57:11,555
And... at the concert...

654
00:57:11,555 --> 00:57:14,439
I think I discovered
an extremely important fact.

655
00:57:16,179 --> 00:57:18,220
Congratulating people
when they're happy,

656
00:57:18,233 --> 00:57:20,284
comforting those
when they're sad...

657
00:57:20,284 --> 00:57:25,758
and a song that doesn't differentiate
between age groups is trot.

658
00:57:27,027 --> 00:57:29,734
I really must be made for trot.

659
00:57:32,227 --> 00:57:34,776
I'm happiest when I sing trot.

660
00:57:36,047 --> 00:57:40,971
So about the ballad album
that you mentioned last time...

661
00:57:40,971 --> 00:57:43,110
Understood.
We'll pretend that never came up.

662
00:57:43,110 --> 00:57:45,017
As expected!

663
00:57:45,017 --> 00:57:47,151
Thank you!

664
00:58:01,572 --> 00:58:07,043
Choi Choon Hee? Yes it was her who was
hospitalized with Jang Joon Hyun.

665
00:58:15,248 --> 00:58:17,920
Has Joon Hyun's memories returned?

666
00:58:17,920 --> 00:58:20,380
Or has he just fallen
for Choi Choon Hee again?

667
00:58:20,380 --> 00:58:22,786
How do we make sure?

668
00:58:22,786 --> 00:58:25,262
Just do as I tell you.

669
00:58:29,742 --> 00:58:31,867
I'll cook it for you.
Go and get changed.

670
00:58:31,867 --> 00:58:33,415
Okay.

671
00:58:58,868 --> 00:59:00,924
Choon Hee.

672
00:59:02,798 --> 00:59:06,844
The strings on my ukelele are fixed.
Did you fix them?

673
00:59:06,844 --> 00:59:08,668
No.

674
00:59:10,422 --> 00:59:13,181
Huh? The fan turns now.

675
00:59:55,458 --> 00:59:57,963
Joon Hyun, I love it.

676
00:59:57,963 --> 01:00:00,139
You bought this for me, right?

677
01:00:00,139 --> 01:00:01,758
It says 'Angel' here.

678
01:00:04,166 --> 01:00:06,417
It wasn't?

679
01:00:08,323 --> 01:00:10,434
What's with your expression, Joon Hyun?

680
01:00:13,034 --> 01:00:16,779
- I'm disappointed in you, Soo In.
- Huh?

681
01:00:23,454 --> 01:00:25,984
I wanted to give it to you properly.

682
01:00:27,283 --> 01:00:29,269
I wanted to see your
surprised expression.

683
01:00:32,232 --> 01:00:34,581
So are you angry, Joon Hyun?

684
01:00:34,581 --> 01:00:37,104
I'm sorry. What do I do?

685
01:00:38,665 --> 01:00:40,917
I'm just kidding.

686
01:00:40,917 --> 01:00:45,491
Why do I have such good taste?
It suits you perfectly.

687
01:00:47,434 --> 01:00:49,526
Seriously.

688
01:01:12,967 --> 01:01:16,305
Good thing you came!
Fix my ukelele strings for me!

689
01:01:16,305 --> 01:01:19,353
- The rotation's broken.
- In this heat?

690
01:01:19,353 --> 01:01:21,351
Watch out!

691
01:02:04,953 --> 01:02:08,917
I'll drink it well.

692
01:03:04,621 --> 01:03:07,114
I'm back.

693
01:03:16,414 --> 01:03:24,414
Subtitles by DramaFever